            </p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@dontwastegroup.com">info@dontwastegroup.com</a></p>
            <p>Website: <a href="http://www.dontwastegroup.com">www.dontwastegroup.com</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
            <p>Quick Links:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Proptech Solution</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Consultancy Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Training</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Tenant Billing & Management Solutions</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Site Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Brokerage</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
